challengeName: CSFV Ghostmap Minisite - Awards Widget Update
detailedRequirements:
Task Requirements

You are making few changes to the Awards widget as outlined below

  • Change the user photo to (text) username (as in the top 10 widget list), username should be href pointing as user profile.
  • Remove the Awarded On column.  
  • The username column should be left jusitified. The awards icons should be centered justified.
  • Add tooltip to award icon "<description> on <date>". where <date> is the removed Awarded On column.

 

Github Private Repo

Files exists in private github repository. If you don't have access to links below, please post in challenge forums to request access.

Source code exists in csfv_minisite_frontend_module (branch minisite4)

Deliverables

  • Patch file of changes.
  • Text file with any notes to reviewer.
